{"tid":1458763,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港首個學生罷課聯盟上線了！","createTime":"2019-08-12T14:57:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T15:36:39.000Z","uid":282535,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"52062622b601d0d6dc02d5de22b763f0a052de59","tid":1458763,"uid":282535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:57:53.000Z","msg":"九月罷課 學生自決<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rPdq6OP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrPdq6OP.jpg&h=722de36a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n六七八月，香港風起，然今煙淚未散而存。過去，中學生發起學生聯署反對送中惡法，甚至以身把淚血拼煙雲，仍是未能得到合理之回應。暑假已臨暮昏，惜送中惡法危機仍存，警、政、民關係更是未嘗得治。開學之日即將上演，我等中學生不能坐以待斃，必須繼續堅持心中的理想，無計可施下，以罷課凝聚中學生力量，讓政府明白，我等非枉讀之輩，稍懂筆墨亦同存良心，敢於環看政治。<br />\n<br />\n雖未讀盡萬卷書，但我等亦願走萬里路，為香港，萬里路比起萬卷書，何重何輕？<br />\n<br />\n故就罷課事宜，香港各大中學生組織包括中學時政、青年前線、悉政學揚、學生動源及學生抗爭力量將成立聯盟，名曰香港學生罷課聯盟。<br />\n<br />\n望能因此喚醒中學生對政治觸覺，讓中學生行使公民責任，勇於發聲，向政府證明中學生力量。同時提升中學生對反修例運動參與度。<br />\n<br />\n蔽盟歡迎各學生組織加入聯盟，僅此望各界支援學生大罷課！<br />\n<br />\n鈞鑒<br />\n天佑香港<br />\n<br />\n香港學生罷課聯盟創始組織<br />\n中學時政<br />\n青年前線<br />\n悉政學揚<br />\n學生動源<br />\n學生抗爭力量<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2019年8月10日<br />\n<br />\n香港學生罷課聯盟Facebook Page<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HongKongStudentStrikeAlliance/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHongKongStudentStrikeAlliance%2F&d=1ZU4T503J%2FBBtE%2F0CauWlYaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=3ccf2725\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HongKongStudentStrikeAlliance/</a><br />\n<br />\n香港學生罷課聯盟Instagram Page<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/studentstrikesept?igshid=14lh92elzufd0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fstudentstrikesept%3Figshid%3D14lh92elzufd0&d=1ZU4T503J%2FBBtE%2F0CauWlYaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=58a4b325\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/studentstrikesept?igshid=14lh92elzufd0</a><br />\n<br />\n香港學生罷課聯盟Telegram Channel <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hongkongstudentstrikealliance\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhongkongstudentstrikealliance&d=1ZU4T503J%2FBBtE%2F0CauWlYaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=b35bf65d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hongkongstudentstrikealliance</a>"},{"pid":"afb3ed825a1fba1edb6eb5262f591867949927e8","tid":1458763,"uid":282535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:59:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">學生罷課學生話事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C9Ut4AM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC9Ut4AM.jpg&h=18c06f62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【自己罷課自已搞｜學生自決 不撒就罷】<br />\n<br />\n九月罷課勢在必行，你又想點為香港未來發聲？<br />\n<br />\n首個由中學生自發，中學生話事，中學生主導嘅反修例大罷課即將上線啦！<br />\n<br />\n依家我哋正在收集大家嘅意見，推動勢在必行嘅全港大罷課，同大家講我哋學生嘅真實主流民意！<br />\n<br />\n自己罷課自己決定！<br />\n齊上齊落&middot;缺一不可！<br />\n<br />\n問卷超連結：<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/dcWxU1PnbH2ND81S8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FdcWxU1PnbH2ND81S8&d=1ZU4T503J%2FBBtE%2F0CauWlYaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=47e1d101\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/dcWxU1PnbH2ND81S8</a>"},{"pid":"15787652e3f3c487f8fd4e1711446042a0f2eae0","tid":1458763,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:02:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2c85c03c4fc367e0aeda17a3e4cab7b7b77ccec","tid":1458763,"uid":282535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:09:18.000Z","msg":"真&middot;學生搞學生罷課<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1604b